When a gossip message arrives at each peer , an image maintenance scheme integrates new records into the current local image and discards excess records such that certain property of the local image is improved ( e.g. , increase overall utility of peers in the image ) Aggregate performance of 45 a gossip mechanism can be presented by two average metrics and their distribution among peers : ( i ) Average Convergence Time : average number of gossip messages until all peers in an overlay reach their final images , and ( ii ) Average Efficiency Ratio : average ratio 